{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDU0ODIwNjM1", "number": 12201, "title": "Notifier: Disable flash notification when off is selected", "bodyText": "I didn't see a bug reported for this so I decided to make a fix it myself.\nWhen the \"Flash Notification\" setting is set to \"Flash until cancelled\" or \"Solid until cancelled\" and the notification goes off, changing the setting to \"Off\" keeps the notification solid even if you move your mouse or click in the game window panel.\nThis fix simply disables any flash notification currently active if the setting is changed to off.", "createdAt": "2020-07-22T01:03:02Z", "url": "https://github.com/runelite/runelite/pull/12201", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "ef86486a82ea64e773c16724b39f8411789687a5"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-08-19T17:51:15Z", "author": {"login": "dereklopes"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 3, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABc3QlsPAFqTQ1MjkzNTE3Ng==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABc-7ozMgBqjM2NTc3NzU0MjI=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NDUyOTM1MTc2", "url": "https://github.com/runelite/runelite/pull/12201#pullrequestreview-452935176", "createdAt": "2020-07-22T01:31:34Z", "commit": {"oid": "64d698a03a116c48dfdc7a15ce80c7bfa1dbfc00"}, "state": "COMMENTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 1, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wNy0yMlQwMTozMTozNFrOG1Pevw==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wNy0yMlQwMTozMTozNFrOG1Pevw==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ1ODQ4MTM0Mw==", "bodyText": "You can just move this up to L211 + move up L217", "url": "https://github.com/runelite/runelite/pull/12201#discussion_r458481343", "createdAt": "2020-07-22T01:31:34Z", "author": {"login": "Adam-"}, "path": "runelite-client/src/main/java/net/runelite/client/Notifier.java